{"tid":1232612,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今次政府脆底，聽日又唔知要跌幾多點","createTime":"2019-06-16T15:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T04:21:23.000Z","uid":66271,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e832cd3b558b3dc0571ff183a4730d73d872e22e","tid":1232612,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7772a6e707c612e57c0fbdb26ae1376fe41808f3","tid":1232612,"uid":76078,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"全港大和解 應該升?"},{"pid":"7fef2602a1b9266a0653f3d8c11d6cab6ea5211e","tid":1232612,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:03:27.000Z","msg":"千跌"},{"pid":"00198bc95a48a4ecf15ebac345280359eb56178c","tid":1232612,"uid":157938,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=97fc038c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ae13ab01e49d443564e21fad39732bafa94a87e","tid":1232612,"uid":126005,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"c1427efbd3b59213e9ed8fa78d8a1a640a7f0b25","tid":1232612,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:43:16.000Z","msg":"呢鋪大撚鑊，香港人咁撚唔聽話，習總要餓撚死香港人喇"},{"pid":"0e18f686e3049d56fa032578167cbedf07c0fa1c","tid":1232612,"uid":133828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e832cd3b558b3dc0571ff183a4730d73d872e22e","tid":1232612,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"點睇期狂守270<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5358f9193a6dc194056e17bf5f28295d3c63d76b","tid":1232612,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e18f686e3049d56fa032578167cbedf07c0fa1c","tid":1232612,"uid":133828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e832cd3b558b3dc0571ff183a4730d73d872e22e","tid":1232612,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"點睇期狂守270<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fefcf8b16310ca9318b9d02bd1f196fcd98b791","tid":1232612,"uid":100337,"like":4,"dis